snippet.title: The End of Warren's House - English Teaser
snippet.description:
It's the first game developed by NBG Studio.
Made with RPG Maker MV, it's a 30/50 minutes long dark graphic adventure, developed to study the game engine.

Available for free at http://www.nbgstudio.com/en/index.php
